# Environment Variables Template

## Firebase Configuration
# Get these values from Firebase Console > Project Settings > General > Your apps > SDK setup and configuration

VITE_FIREBASE_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
VITE_FIREBASE_AUTH_DOMAIN=your_project_id.firebaseapp.com
VITE_FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=your_project_id
VITE_FIREBASE_STORAGE_BUCKET=your_project_id.appspot.com
VITE_FIREBASE_MESSAGING_SENDER_ID=your_sender_id
VITE_FIREBASE_APP_ID=your_app_id
VITE_FIREBASE_MEASUREMENT_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX

## Optional: Sentry Error Monitoring (Free Tier)
# VITE_SENTRY_DSN=https://your-sentry-dsn@sentry.io/project-id

## Instructions
# 1. Copy this file to `.env.local`
# 2. Replace all values with your actual Firebase configuration
# 3. NEVER commit `.env.local` to version control
# 4. Restart dev server after making changes
